messages.text: Did you hear what happened to Jordan?
Yeah, Friday night after the game. He was run over or shot or something
Yeah, the cops are looking into it
She says that they found his body in the senior lot
She saw it because she had to drop off cheerleading stuff after the game
She saw a few other cars in the lot
She doesn’t remember anybody else’s car?
She might have but didn’t tell me
I think she’s at the police station now
That’s why she’s not responding to my texts
Who do you think could have done it?
You think it was a student?
I don’t know but it happened in the senior lot
I don’t know who else would be there at that time, you know?
Who would have something against him?
He’s always gettin into it with Luke
Yeah but I don’t think it’s that bad
That’s why it could be him!
I don’t know if it’s true
But at the end of the game
When Shelly went to tell Jordan congrats
He told her that he saw Mr. Heffington talking to some girl
He said it was like they were flirting
Like they were together or something. It was weird
Did he see who she was?
Do you think she told the cops that?
Why? Do you think it matters?
I always thought there was something weird about him
I had him for social studies
That’s right. We took it together
Didn’t you think he was weird?
I thought he was cute lol
He was weird and a little scary
I also heard he had a past
Like he used to live out of state
And he hitch hiked all the way here
He was an alcoholic or something
Then he met Mrs. Reynolds and she helped him get a teaching job and stuff
But don’t you think it’s weird?
I remember him hanging out by the girl’s locker room
A week or two ago after PE
We saw Mr. Heffington, like he was waiting for somebody
It was weird because we thought he was a new student at first
Jordan got a look at him and I think Mr. Heffington saw him but he didn’t see me
So it was after second period?
That’s right. You have it after me lol
What happened after you guys saw him?
You didn’t see who he was waiting for?
Brianna told me she saw you talking to Mr. Heffington after school one time
She said she saw you two hugging
That was like a month ago
But you took social studies with me last quarter
You think Shelly is still talking to the police?
Why did you ask me that just now?
LIKE I SAID HE WAS HELPING ME WITH HOMEWORK!!!
Was he waiting for you before PE?
It was another rumor about him
That he was dating a student
Just another thing like how he hitch hiked here from Alabama
You’re not going to tell the cops are you?
Because I know you’re at home
